description:
We put together a 75 minute compilation of all our How I Met Your Mother videos. Hope you enjoy! 

How I Met Your Mother is a show that could be researched forever.  Throughout it's nine season run, How I Met Your Mother climbed the mountain top of primetime network sitcoms, but had an equally hard fall from grace.  Lets take a look and breakdown all the How I Met Your Mother we have to offer.

#howimetyourmother #barneystinson #tedmosby #nerdstalgic
title: Breaking Down The Highs And Lows Of How I Met Your Mother | Compilation
